{
  "video_id": "wmE8dQcZgB4",
  "title": "This company pays kids to do their math homework | Mohamad Jebara",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13560.0,
      "end_time": 17410.0,
      "text": "For as long as I remember, I&#39;ve loved mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18240.0,
      "end_time": 20311.0,
      "text": "Actually, it&#39;s not 100 percent true."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20919.0,
      "end_time": 24263.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve loved mathematics for all but a two-week period"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24287.0,
      "end_time": 25445.0,
      "text": "in senior high school."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25469.0,
      "end_time": 26783.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26807.0,
      "end_time": 27980.0,
      "text": "I was top of my class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28500.0,
      "end_time": 30787.0,
      "text": "and we were about to start the Extension Maths course."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30811.0,
      "end_time": 34730.0,
      "text": "I was really excited about this brand new topic coming up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34970.0,
      "end_time": 35247.0,
      "text": "complex numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36640.0,
      "end_time": 37214.0,
      "text": "I like complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38112.0,
      "end_time": 40120.0,
      "text": "My teacher was priming us for the concepts"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 40144.0,
      "end_time": 42217.0,
      "text": "with some questions about square roots."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42241.0,
      "end_time": 44740.0,
      "text": "Square of nine -- three;"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44980.0,
      "end_time": 46114.0,
      "text": "square of 256 -- sixteen."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 46852.0,
      "end_time": 48100.0,
      "text": "Too easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48360.0,
      "end_time": 50448.0,
      "text": "Then she asked the trick question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50472.0,
      "end_time": 53920.0,
      "text": "What about the square root of negative one?"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53809.0,
      "end_time": 55452.0,
      "text": "Of course, we were all over it --"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55476.0,
      "end_time": 56627.0,
      "text": "\"Come on, Miss!"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 56651.0,
      "end_time": 59380.0,
      "text": "We all know you can&#39;t take the square root of a negative.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 59841.0,
      "end_time": 61856.0,
      "text": "\"That&#39;s true in the real world,\" she said."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 62238.0,
      "end_time": 64770.0,
      "text": "\"But in the complex world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 64101.0,
      "end_time": 68333.0,
      "text": "the square root of negative one is the imaginary number i.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 69879.0,
      "end_time": 72633.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 72657.0,
      "end_time": 73836.0,
      "text": "That day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 73860.0,
      "end_time": 76863.0,
      "text": "my entire mathematical world came crashing down on me."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 76887.0,
      "end_time": 78235.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 78259.0,
      "end_time": 79632.0,
      "text": "\"Imaginary numbers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 79974.0,
      "end_time": 81124.0,
      "text": "Seriously?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 81490.0,
      "end_time": 83475.0,
      "text": "But mathematics is a source of truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 83499.0,
      "end_time": 85276.0,
      "text": "please don&#39;t go abstract on me."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85831.0,
      "end_time": 87679.0,
      "text": "I would have studied art"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 87703.0,
      "end_time": 89974.0,
      "text": "if I wanted to play with imaginary numbers.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 89998.0,
      "end_time": 91641.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 91665.0,
      "end_time": 94494.0,
      "text": "\"This is Extension Maths, let&#39;s get back with our program!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 94998.0,
      "end_time": 96156.0,
      "text": "She didn&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 96180.0,
      "end_time": 97958.0,
      "text": "and over the next couple of weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 97982.0,
      "end_time": 101229.0,
      "text": "I reluctantly performed meaningless calculations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 101253.0,
      "end_time": 102254.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 102278.0,
      "end_time": 105221.0,
      "text": "finding imaginary solutions to quadratic equations."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 105245.0,
      "end_time": 106857.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 106881.0,
      "end_time": 108897.0,
      "text": "But then something amazing happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 108921.0,
      "end_time": 111732.0,
      "text": "We began finding elegant solutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 111756.0,
      "end_time": 115661.0,
      "text": "to real-world problems we previously had no answers to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 115685.0,
      "end_time": 118799.0,
      "text": "starting with the complex world of imaginary numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 119758.0,
      "end_time": 122514.0,
      "text": "So some mathematician 500 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 122538.0,
      "end_time": 126640.0,
      "text": "decides to have some fun and make up these imaginary numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 126665.0,
      "end_time": 131649.0,
      "text": "and because of that we can now derive these amazing identities"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131673.0,
      "end_time": 133457.0,
      "text": "with applications in the real world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 133481.0,
      "end_time": 135703.0,
      "text": "in fields like electrical engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136379.0,
      "end_time": 137593.0,
      "text": "Wow!"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 137617.0,
      "end_time": 141257.0,
      "text": "I gained a whole new level of appreciation for mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141858.0,
      "end_time": 144880.0,
      "text": "And after my brief mistrust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 144112.0,
      "end_time": 147512.0,
      "text": "I was now in love with the subject more than ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148711.0,
      "end_time": 152959.0,
      "text": "Francis Su, the mathematician, sums it up beautifully when he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 152983.0,
      "end_time": 157530.0,
      "text": "\"We study mathematics for play, for beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 157770.0,
      "end_time": 158339.0,
      "text": "for truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 158363.0,
      "end_time": 160530.0,
      "text": "for justice and for love.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 161458.0,
      "end_time": 163355.0,
      "text": "But if you ask a student today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 163379.0,
      "end_time": 165322.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll probably hear a different story."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 165828.0,
      "end_time": 167748.0,
      "text": "You might hear \"difficult\" and \"boring.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 168264.0,
      "end_time": 170780.0,
      "text": "And they might be right about difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 170804.0,
      "end_time": 173367.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s certainly not boring."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 173939.0,
      "end_time": 176560.0,
      "text": "In fact, I&#39;d say being difficult to master"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 176584.0,
      "end_time": 178641.0,
      "text": "is part of what makes it beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 178958.0,
      "end_time": 181358.0,
      "text": "Because nothing worth doing is easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 182300.0,
      "end_time": 186196.0,
      "text": "So we need students to stick around long enough through the difficult parts"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 186220.0,
      "end_time": 189710.0,
      "text": "to appreciate the beauty when it all ties together."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 189522.0,
      "end_time": 192640.0,
      "text": "Much like I did for that brief couple of weeks in high school."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 194768.0,
      "end_time": 197293.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, our school systems --"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 197950.0,
      "end_time": 201417.0,
      "text": "we move students through mathematics in a lockstep process."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 201442.0,
      "end_time": 203850.0,
      "text": "So those who fall a little behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 203109.0,
      "end_time": 206772.0,
      "text": "find it near impossible to ever catch up and appreciate that beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 208500.0,
      "end_time": 209363.0,
      "text": "But why is this a problem?"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 209387.0,
      "end_time": 210632.0,
      "text": "Why should we care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 211355.0,
      "end_time": 212855.0,
      "text": "Well today, more than ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 212879.0,
      "end_time": 216450.0,
      "text": "our world needs every citizen to be skilled in mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 217610.0,
      "end_time": 220514.0,
      "text": "With the advent of artificial intelligence and automation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 220538.0,
      "end_time": 223515.0,
      "text": "many of the jobs we see today will either not exist"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 223539.0,
      "end_time": 226910.0,
      "text": "or be transformed to require less routine work"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 226934.0,
      "end_time": 229793.0,
      "text": "and more analysis and application of expertise."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 230474.0,
      "end_time": 232998.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re not producing the extra mathematics students"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 233220.0,
      "end_time": 234275.0,
      "text": "to fill these new roles."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 234300.0,
      "end_time": 236291.0,
      "text": "This graph shows the number of students"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 236315.0,
      "end_time": 238926.0,
      "text": "taking Standard Mathematics"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 238950.0,
      "end_time": 241203.0,
      "text": "and Advanced Mathematics"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 241228.0,
      "end_time": 243815.0,
      "text": "over a period of 20 years in Australia."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 243839.0,
      "end_time": 249252.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s clear that while we have demand for mathematics skills rapidly increasing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 249276.0,
      "end_time": 252650.0,
      "text": "supply is in steady decline."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 253728.0,
      "end_time": 255410.0,
      "text": "To put things in perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 255434.0,
      "end_time": 260498.0,
      "text": "half of the students completing high school today in Australia"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 260522.0,
      "end_time": 263195.0,
      "text": "are not prepared to understand any argument"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 263220.0,
      "end_time": 265220.0,
      "text": "about rates of change in data."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 266363.0,
      "end_time": 268530.0,
      "text": "In this digital age"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 268770.0,
      "end_time": 271990.0,
      "text": "where fake news can influence election results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 272140.0,
      "end_time": 274482.0,
      "text": "this is very concerning."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 275458.0,
      "end_time": 277149.0,
      "text": "Let me give you a concrete example."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 277173.0,
      "end_time": 279172.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s take a closer look at that graph."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 279673.0,
      "end_time": 282712.0,
      "text": "Can everyone see what I&#39;ve done there to stress my point?"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 282736.0,
      "end_time": 285847.0,
      "text": "If you can&#39;t, let me show you now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 285871.0,
      "end_time": 288751.0,
      "text": "with the vertical axis starting at zero, where it should be."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 289323.0,
      "end_time": 290926.0,
      "text": "There, you see it now, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 290950.0,
      "end_time": 292837.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the exact same data"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 292862.0,
      "end_time": 296523.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;ve manipulated the representation to influence you."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299149.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s cool, that&#39;s my job up here."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 299173.0,
      "end_time": 300174.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 300198.0,
      "end_time": 301714.0,
      "text": "But in all seriousness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 301738.0,
      "end_time": 303480.0,
      "text": "unless we do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 303720.0,
      "end_time": 306696.0,
      "text": "to drastically improve student engagement with mathematics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 306720.0,
      "end_time": 309989.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll not only have a huge skills shortage crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 310130.0,
      "end_time": 312292.0,
      "text": "but a fickle population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 312316.0,
      "end_time": 315893.0,
      "text": "easily manipulated by whoever can get the most air time."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 317759.0,
      "end_time": 319760.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s the solution?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 319760.0,
      "end_time": 321860.0,
      "text": "There are a lot of things we have to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 321884.0,
      "end_time": 323844.0,
      "text": "We need curriculum reform."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 323868.0,
      "end_time": 327448.0,
      "text": "We need our best and brightest encouraged to become teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 327764.0,
      "end_time": 330315.0,
      "text": "We need to put an end to high-stakes tests"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 330339.0,
      "end_time": 333126.0,
      "text": "and instead follow a mastery-based learning approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 333617.0,
      "end_time": 336230.0,
      "text": "But all these things take time."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 337157.0,
      "end_time": 339140.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m impatient."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 340415.0,
      "end_time": 343770.0,
      "text": "See, I&#39;ve been thinking about this for eight years now."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 343101.0,
      "end_time": 346355.0,
      "text": "Ever since I left my job as a derivative trader"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 346379.0,
      "end_time": 349825.0,
      "text": "to build a web application to help students learn mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 350585.0,
      "end_time": 354510.0,
      "text": "Today, our app is used by schools across the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 354411.0,
      "end_time": 355998.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re seeing big improvements"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 356220.0,
      "end_time": 358228.0,
      "text": "for students who use the program regularly."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 359140.0,
      "end_time": 360649.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s the thing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 360673.0,
      "end_time": 365418.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re only seeing it for students who use the program regularly."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 366276.0,
      "end_time": 368216.0,
      "text": "And most of them don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 369212.0,
      "end_time": 373180.0,
      "text": "So after years of developing and refining the application,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 373204.0,
      "end_time": 376299.0,
      "text": "our biggest challenge was not so much product related,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 376323.0,
      "end_time": 378959.0,
      "text": "our biggest challenge was motivating students"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 378983.0,
      "end_time": 382640.0,
      "text": "to want to work on their gaps in understanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 383688.0,
      "end_time": 385870.0,
      "text": "You can imagine in today&#39;s attention economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 385894.0,
      "end_time": 389530.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re competing against Facebook, Snapchat and PlayStation"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 389770.0,
      "end_time": 391810.0,
      "text": "to try and get these students&#39; time."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 391982.0,
      "end_time": 393704.0,
      "text": "So we went back to the drawing board"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 393728.0,
      "end_time": 396521.0,
      "text": "and started to think about how we could make it worthwhile"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 396545.0,
      "end_time": 400450.0,
      "text": "for students to spend some of their \"attention budget\""
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 400690.0,
      "end_time": 401336.0,
      "text": "on their education."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 402244.0,
      "end_time": 404395.0,
      "text": "We tinkered with gamification elements"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 404419.0,
      "end_time": 407267.0,
      "text": "like points, badges and avatars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 407291.0,
      "end_time": 410133.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;d see a temporary spike in engagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 410157.0,
      "end_time": 413373.0,
      "text": "but things would go back to normal as soon as the novelty wore off."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 414466.0,
      "end_time": 416387.0,
      "text": "Then one day, my cofounder, Alvin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 416411.0,
      "end_time": 419290.0,
      "text": "came across a study of students in Chicago"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 419530.0,
      "end_time": 421831.0,
      "text": "led by the behavioral economist, Steven Levitt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 421855.0,
      "end_time": 424831.0,
      "text": "where they paid students who improved on their test scores."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 426474.0,
      "end_time": 429569.0,
      "text": "He started telling me about some of the things they tested for"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 429593.0,
      "end_time": 431407.0,
      "text": "and the interesting findings they had."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 432300.0,
      "end_time": 437323.0,
      "text": "For instance, they found that incentivizing students for inputs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 437347.0,
      "end_time": 438625.0,
      "text": "like effort,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 438649.0,
      "end_time": 442220.0,
      "text": "worked a lot better than incentivizing for outputs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 442460.0,
      "end_time": 443195.0,
      "text": "like test scores."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 444188.0,
      "end_time": 447719.0,
      "text": "They found that for younger students, you could win them over with a trophy"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 447744.0,
      "end_time": 449276.0,
      "text": "but for older students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 449300.0,
      "end_time": 450879.0,
      "text": "you really needed cash."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 450903.0,
      "end_time": 452252.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 452276.0,
      "end_time": 454990.0,
      "text": "And the amount of cash mattered -- 10 dollars was good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 455140.0,
      "end_time": 456747.0,
      "text": "20 dollars -- even better."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 458770.0,
      "end_time": 460109.0,
      "text": "But perhaps most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 460133.0,
      "end_time": 462688.0,
      "text": "they found that the rewards had to be instant"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 462712.0,
      "end_time": 464743.0,
      "text": "rather than promised at a later date."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 465379.0,
      "end_time": 468379.0,
      "text": "They went as far as to give the students 20 dollars and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 468403.0,
      "end_time": 470410.0,
      "text": "\"Touch it, feel it, smell it --\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 470434.0,
      "end_time": 471680.0,
      "text": "(Sniffing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 471704.0,
      "end_time": 472854.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s all yours."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 473442.0,
      "end_time": 475664.0,
      "text": "But if you fail, I&#39;m going to take it back.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 475688.0,
      "end_time": 477555.0,
      "text": "And that worked really well."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 479330.0,
      "end_time": 480603.0,
      "text": "I immediately got excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 480627.0,
      "end_time": 483862.0,
      "text": "about the possibilities of implementing this in our program."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 483886.0,
      "end_time": 485879.0,
      "text": "But once the excitement settled down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 485903.0,
      "end_time": 488633.0,
      "text": "there were a few concerns that crept in our minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 488657.0,
      "end_time": 490440.0,
      "text": "Firstly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 490690.0,
      "end_time": 491299.0,
      "text": "was this ethical?"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 491741.0,
      "end_time": 492757.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 492781.0,
      "end_time": 495561.0,
      "text": "Secondly, how would we fund this thing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 495585.0,
      "end_time": 496736.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 496760.0,
      "end_time": 497933.0,
      "text": "And finally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 497958.0,
      "end_time": 501180.0,
      "text": "would the results be sustained if the students were no longer paid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 501911.0,
      "end_time": 503950.0,
      "text": "Now, let&#39;s look at the ethical part first."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 503974.0,
      "end_time": 505840.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a bit of a mathematical purist."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 505864.0,
      "end_time": 509599.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;d be one of the first people to say that we should study mathematics"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 509624.0,
      "end_time": 511491.0,
      "text": "for the sake of mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 511861.0,
      "end_time": 516570.0,
      "text": "Remember -- for play, for beauty, for truth, for justice and for love!"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 516780.0,
      "end_time": 517939.0,
      "text": "Not for money!"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 517964.00000000006,
      "end_time": 519178.00000000006,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 519202.0,
      "end_time": 521307.0,
      "text": "As I struggled with this, I came to see that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 521331.0,
      "end_time": 523401.0,
      "text": "while it&#39;s a way I look at mathematics now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 523424.0,
      "end_time": 526322.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s only because I studied it long enough to appreciate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 527380.0,
      "end_time": 530649.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very difficult to tell a student struggling with mathematics today"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 530673.0,
      "end_time": 533719.0,
      "text": "to work hard for a payoff in the distant future."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 534306.0,
      "end_time": 536677.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not so much bribery that&#39;s at work here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 536701.0,
      "end_time": 538242.0,
      "text": "because I could bribe students"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 538266.0,
      "end_time": 542402.0,
      "text": "by telling them about my big bonuses in my derivative trading days"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 542427.0,
      "end_time": 544291.0,
      "text": "as a reward for doing well at maths."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 544831.0,
      "end_time": 547259.0,
      "text": "But it doesn&#39;t pay off for a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 547592.0,
      "end_time": 549223.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s practically naught."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 550149.0,
      "end_time": 553148.0,
      "text": "Behavioral economists call this hyperbolic discounting."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 553760.0,
      "end_time": 555863.0,
      "text": "And Levitt goes as far as to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 555887.0,
      "end_time": 558958.0,
      "text": "that all motivating power vanishes"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 558982.0,
      "end_time": 561156.0,
      "text": "when rewards are handed out with a delay."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 561720.0,
      "end_time": 566490.0,
      "text": "So, from a purely economic point of view:"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 566514.0,
      "end_time": 569942.0,
      "text": "if we don&#39;t use immediate incentives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 569966.0,
      "end_time": 572480.0,
      "text": "we are underinvesting in student outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 573474.0,
      "end_time": 576315.0,
      "text": "I took heart from that, and came to see that as a society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 576339.0,
      "end_time": 578879.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re actually quite used to financial incentives."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 578903.0,
      "end_time": 582690.0,
      "text": "Whether it be by the government, by employers or at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 582966.0,
      "end_time": 585365.0,
      "text": "For instance, many parents would pay their children"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 585389.0,
      "end_time": 588190.0,
      "text": "an allowance or pocket money for doing chores in the house."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 588557.0,
      "end_time": 591410.0,
      "text": "So it wasn&#39;t really all that controversial."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 591954.0,
      "end_time": 593128.0,
      "text": "As I thought about that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 593153.0,
      "end_time": 596875.0,
      "text": "it started to answer that second question of how we were going to fund this."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 596899.0,
      "end_time": 600394.0,
      "text": "Naturally, parents are the most invested in their children&#39;s education."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 601750.0,
      "end_time": 604601.0,
      "text": "So, let&#39;s charge them a weekly subscription fee"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 604625.0,
      "end_time": 606323.0,
      "text": "to use our program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 606347.0,
      "end_time": 607641.0,
      "text": "but --"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 607665.0,
      "end_time": 610641.0,
      "text": "if the students complete their weekly maths goal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 610665.0,
      "end_time": 615541.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll refund the subscription amount directly into the child&#39;s bank account."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 616855.0,
      "end_time": 619688.0,
      "text": "We chose three exercises completed"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 619712.0,
      "end_time": 621459.0,
      "text": "over a one week period"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 621483.0,
      "end_time": 623160.0,
      "text": "for a 10 dollar reward."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 623641.0,
      "end_time": 627680.0,
      "text": "That way we&#39;re incentivizing effort rather than performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 627704.0,
      "end_time": 629489.0,
      "text": "over a short enough period"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 629514.0,
      "end_time": 632614.0,
      "text": "and with a substantial enough payout for the students to care."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 633576.0,
      "end_time": 637290.0,
      "text": "Now, I remember when I first told my wife about this new business model."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 637917.0,
      "end_time": 642712.0,
      "text": "If she had any doubt left that I&#39;ve gone completely mad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 642736.0,
      "end_time": 645269.0,
      "text": "that pretty much confirmed it for her."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 645703.0,
      "end_time": 647212.0,
      "text": "She said to me, \"Mo ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 647236.0,
      "end_time": 651600.0,
      "text": "you realize that if everybody does their homework, which you want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 651300.0,
      "end_time": 654290.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not going to make any revenue, which you don&#39;t want."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 654530.0,
      "end_time": 655513.0,
      "text": "Great business model.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 655537.0,
      "end_time": 656742.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 656766.0,
      "end_time": 659146.0,
      "text": "I say it&#39;s more like an antibusiness model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 659170.0,
      "end_time": 661949.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s free if you use it, but you pay if you don&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 663101.0,
      "end_time": 664704.0,
      "text": "Now, I knew from experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 664728.0,
      "end_time": 667260.0,
      "text": "that not everybody in the country was going to jump on"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 667284.0,
      "end_time": 669164.0,
      "text": "and do their maths homework every week."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 669188.0,
      "end_time": 671760.0,
      "text": "And if they did, sure we&#39;d go bust pretty quickly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 671784.0,
      "end_time": 675496.0,
      "text": "but hey, we would have solved the country&#39;s maths skills crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 675520.0,
      "end_time": 677790.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 677815.0,
      "end_time": 680299.0,
      "text": "As a company, we&#39;ve always run a double bottom line,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 680323.0,
      "end_time": 682363.0,
      "text": "looking to both make a return for investors"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 682387.0,
      "end_time": 684790.0,
      "text": "as well as improve student outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 684815.0,
      "end_time": 687474.0,
      "text": "We know that our path to long-term profitability"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 687498.0,
      "end_time": 689641.0,
      "text": "is through improving student outcomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 689665.0,
      "end_time": 692214.0,
      "text": "So our dual objectives should never be at odds."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 695701.0,
      "end_time": 698352.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re always looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 698376.0,
      "end_time": 699788.0,
      "text": "to make our product decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 699812.0,
      "end_time": 702672.0,
      "text": "around helping students reach their weekly maths goal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 702696.0,
      "end_time": 705529.0,
      "text": "effectively ensuring that they get paid"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 705553.0,
      "end_time": 706703.0,
      "text": "and not us."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 707370.0,
      "end_time": 710575.0,
      "text": "Now you must be wondering: How is this crazy business model going?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 711934.0,
      "end_time": 714425.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll be glad to know we&#39;re still in business."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 714450.0,
      "end_time": 717290.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been testing this now for the last five months"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 717530.0,
      "end_time": 719426.0,
      "text": "on just our personal home users in Australia"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 719450.0,
      "end_time": 722117.0,
      "text": "before we think about rolling it out to schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 722141.0,
      "end_time": 723942.0,
      "text": "And here are the early results."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 724776.0,
      "end_time": 728410.0,
      "text": "The green represents students who are completing their weekly maths goal"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 728434.0,
      "end_time": 729863.0,
      "text": "and the red those who aren&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 730315.0,
      "end_time": 733497.0,
      "text": "You can see a lot more completing their homework than not."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 733521.0,
      "end_time": 735934.0,
      "text": "In fact, as our user base has grown,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 735958.0,
      "end_time": 739584.0,
      "text": "we found the percentage to be pretty steady, at around 75 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 739609.0,
      "end_time": 743690.0,
      "text": "So on average, we receive our weekly subscription fee"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 743930.0,
      "end_time": 745290.0,
      "text": "once every four weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 745315.0,
      "end_time": 748323.0,
      "text": "and the other three weeks, we&#39;re rewarding the students."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 749386.0,
      "end_time": 752690.0,
      "text": "Now of course we&#39;re leaving some money on the table here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 752940.0,
      "end_time": 753245.0,
      "text": "but guess what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 753269.0,
      "end_time": 755196.0,
      "text": "It turns out these students"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 755220.0,
      "end_time": 760484.0,
      "text": "are 70 percent more engaged than students not on the reward program."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 761109.0,
      "end_time": 762259.0,
      "text": "Check."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 764600.0,
      "end_time": 766236.0,
      "text": "From a business perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 766260.0,
      "end_time": 768172.0,
      "text": "they are less likely to churn"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 768196.0,
      "end_time": 770180.0,
      "text": "and more likely to refer friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 770204.0,
      "end_time": 773839.0,
      "text": "so we&#39;re hoping to trade off a lower revenue per user"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 773863.0,
      "end_time": 776530.0,
      "text": "for a bigger and more engaged user base."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 776895.0,
      "end_time": 778307.0,
      "text": "Check and check."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 779484.0,
      "end_time": 781286.0,
      "text": "Now for that final question."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 781310.0,
      "end_time": 784159.0,
      "text": "Would they keep coming back if they were no longer paid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 784754.0,
      "end_time": 788277.0,
      "text": "Mathematics is so much more than just a subject you study at school."
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 788897.0,
      "end_time": 790364.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a human endeavor."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 790823.0,
      "end_time": 793766.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s what helps us to understand the world around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 794690.0,
      "end_time": 797450.0,
      "text": "And the more you know, the more you want to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 797632.0,
      "end_time": 800656.0,
      "text": "So yes, we&#39;ve triggered initial engagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 800681.0,
      "end_time": 802540.0,
      "text": "with a financial reward."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 802649.0,
      "end_time": 804850.0,
      "text": "But in the long run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 804109.0,
      "end_time": 806100.0,
      "text": "the money won&#39;t matter anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 806340.0,
      "end_time": 807685.0,
      "text": "Because in the long run,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 807709.0,
      "end_time": 810819.0,
      "text": "the wonder of mathematics will be the incentive"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 810844.0,
      "end_time": 812463.0,
      "text": "and understanding it"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 812487.0,
      "end_time": 813752.0,
      "text": "will be the reward."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 814342.0,
      "end_time": 815516.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 815541.0,
      "end_time": 820333.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}